00:55:30,170 --> 00:55:31,970
Emi!
Emi!

381
00:55:35,910 --> 00:55:37,570
Emi!
Emi!

382
00:55:39,180 --> 00:55:39,910
Emi.

383
00:55:49,190 --> 00:55:51,850
Tati... pojď.

384
00:55:57,730 --> 00:56:00,830
Mami... už jde.

385
00:56:03,470 --> 00:56:05,410
Zase můžeme žít spolu.

386
00:56:14,880 --> 00:56:18,820
Tati... co to děláš?
Pojď dovnitř.

387
00:56:19,420 --> 00:56:20,120
Emi...

388
00:56:26,400 --> 00:56:27,620
Kdo jsi?

